lead_paragraph: Maccabi Tel Aviv forward Eran Zahavi signed a deal with Chinese side Guangzhou for an Israeli record transfer fee of $8 million (5.94 million pounds) on Wednesday, Maccabi said.

headline.print_headline: Israeli Forward Zahavi Signs for Chinese Side Guangzhou
